data.title: Cascade Communications?
data.meta_description: Anybody still running Cascade / Ascend / Lucent STDX / B-STDX / CX 500 or 550 layer-2 switches? They did Frame Relay and ATM. I spied one behind glass in the data center where my company keeps their presence.
data.text:
Anybody still running Cascade / Ascend / Lucent STDX / B-STDX / CX 500 or 550 layer-2 switches? They did Frame Relay and ATM. I spied one behind glass in the data center where my company keeps their presence.

Worked for them back in the day doing sustaining support. Good times. Got my foundation in the release process before the idea of continuous rebuild was done.
